I mean, I'm sure it was a real big story of how the Decimators of Dragons

264
00:13:51,040 --> 00:13:53,920
saved her from an ice dragon's lair.

265
00:13:53,920 --> 00:13:55,680
A tale told across the land.

266
00:13:56,880 --> 00:13:58,720
Yeah, that one lasted 20 years.

267
00:13:58,720 --> 00:14:03,759
Yeah. But yeah, you would recognize it.

268
00:14:04,800 --> 00:14:15,519
I would like to do a quick sweep of this building if you have the time to spare, but

269
00:14:17,440 --> 00:14:24,000
I would not object to joining you in Icewind Dale if that is where the Brotherhood now is.

270
00:14:25,519 --> 00:14:26,960
I'm happy to wait.

271
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:29,519
I think we could use all the help we can get.

272
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:32,240
Also, can I touch your horse?

273
00:14:33,280 --> 00:14:34,560
I would not recommend it.

274
