00:54:57,440 --> 00:55:01,120
How are you breaking through at least the first few undead?

1027
00:55:01,119 --> 00:55:08,159
So building up as much speed as possible on the way down

1028
00:55:08,159 --> 00:55:10,880
sort of hunched over Rex's neck

1029
00:55:10,880 --> 00:55:13,599
sort of sitting high in the saddle.

1030
00:55:13,599 --> 00:55:14,719
Shield on one arm.

1031
00:55:14,719 --> 00:55:16,880
I'm going to pull the mace in the other

1032
00:55:16,880 --> 00:55:19,199
and like stay silent as long as possible

1033
00:55:19,199 --> 00:55:23,759
because I think they're sort of focused on the wall.

1034
00:55:24,480 --> 00:55:24,960
Just like that.

1035
00:55:24,960 --> 00:55:27,440
But at the last minute I think you know

1036
00:55:27,440 --> 00:55:28,960
the joy kind of overtakes her

1037
00:55:28,960 --> 00:55:32,159
and she'll just like let out a giant scream

1038
00:55:32,159 --> 00:55:34,960
as she like just barrels into them.

1039
00:55:34,960 --> 00:55:37,119
And I mean he's a charger.

1040
00:55:37,119 --> 00:55:39,599
He's like a half demonic warhorse.

1041
00:55:39,599 --> 00:55:44,079
So like we trample the first few for sure

1042
00:55:44,079 --> 00:55:45,199
and just I'm just going to like

1043
00:55:46,000 --> 00:55:49,519
it's like playing T-ball with the mace.

1044
00:55:51,920 --> 00:55:52,420
Heads.

1045
00:55:54,079 --> 00:55:57,760
This massive horse and goliath are charging through

1046
00:55:57,760 --> 00:55:59,200
and heads are flying

1047
00:55:59,920 --> 00:56:04,800
and then you see a goth reach the wall

1048
00:56:05,920 --> 00:56:09,040
and it begins to light up.

1049
00:56:10,240 --> 00:56:14,000
It didn't do this when Yenbul charged through.

1050
00:56:15,040 --> 00:56:16,960
Like the horse hits this wall

1051
00:56:17,520 --> 00:56:20,880
and flames begin shooting out and around.

1052
00:56:22,320 --> 00:56:24,560
She continues to charge forward

1053
00:56:24,559 --> 00:56:27,199
and Yenbul you see like this horse

1054
00:56:28,719 --> 00:56:30,960
and a goth you would see it too.

1055
00:56:30,960 --> 00:56:34,799
Like the flesh begin to bubble

1056
00:56:35,920 --> 00:56:39,519
and you feel like you hit like quicksand.

1057
00:56:41,039 --> 00:56:43,759
Like you slow a lot

1058
00:56:43,759 --> 00:56:46,719
and you feel the undead grasping

1059
00:56:46,719 --> 00:56:48,320
for your horse behind you

1060
00:56:48,320 --> 00:56:50,799
and kind of pulling through with you

1061
00:56:50,799 --> 00:56:53,279
as you are continuing your momentum

1062
00:56:53,280 --> 00:56:55,120
as much as you can through.

1063
00:56:55,120 --> 00:56:59,840
And Yenbul you hear the whistling sound

1064
00:56:59,840 --> 00:57:02,880
of an arrow flying through the air towards you.

